Detailed Description

============================================================================

CSL CPSW API has implementation for multiple SoCs with below SoC map

  1. cpsw v0 - SOC_K2H/SOC_K2K
  2. cpsw v1 - SOC_K2E/SOC_K2L
  3. cpsw v2 - SOC_K2G
  4. cpsw v3 - SOC_AM574x/SOC_AM572x/SOC_AM571x/SOC_DRA75X/SOC_DRA78X
  5. cpsw v4 - SOC_C6678
Note
: there may not be any ip specific implementation for that soc, if it contains only cslr_* files
